Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾形游紀的綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓倒性的耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,征服所有觀眾的那光芒使她成為了絕對的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的舞者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓倒性的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從照片中看著她的身影 我追尋著那微微感覺到的光芒而舞蹈著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了追上母親
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓我的存在消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 當那已經不可能實現的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.36,0:00:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當失去了認為是自己全部生命的芭蕾的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子來到了我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.27,0:01:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祥子那一如既往的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我所僅剩的唯一光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘著Fuego時看到的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激昂的興奮感和翱翔於空中的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為找到了已不能再跳舞的雙腳的替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我想錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個錯誤傷害到了他人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害到了重要的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓重要的朋友為之死去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:58.75,LOGO1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:58.75,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,300)}{\fad(0,1700)}極影&薔薇園
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:00.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:00.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上機車 馬力全開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:03.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:03.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}試著去感受心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:07.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:07.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飛躍吧！盡你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:10.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:10.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸騰有如泉湧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:14.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:14.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我們的週遭佈滿陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:18.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:18.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用淚水洗去血染的污點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:21.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:21.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}讓雙眼避開所有的蠱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:24.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:24.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之風會引領我們向前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:41.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:41.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:45.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:45.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波濤洶湧的世界裡找尋指引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:49.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:49.88,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}舉目看 天湛藍 縱然世界狂亂不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:51.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:51.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背騎的身影穿梭其間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:54.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:54.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我們需要的是你們的共鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:57.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:57.38,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去創造屬於我們的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:00.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:00.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真實 我與它們融與一體
