Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠代前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾形
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rideback部隊離基地大門還有2000米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統發生異常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有從內部入侵的可能
